{"tid":2076360,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"只有遊戲能讓金希澈花錢！自爆手遊課金100萬　這次直接投資一支電競戰隊","createTime":"2020-06-23T12:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T00:58:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6f404fa7bcd26376f3beac609822e9fc829ecd21","tid":2076360,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:39:40.000Z","msg":"「韓流始祖」Super Junior成員金希澈是出名的遊戲迷，除了喜歡打線上遊戲外，更曾透露自己曾經在手遊上花了4000萬韓元（約台幣100萬）。被粉絲戲稱「只在遊戲花錢的哥」，金希澈這回更是直接投資了一支職業電競隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n不只當課金戰士，據韓媒報導，金希澈近日投資了「英雄聯盟」職業電競隊伍Brion Esports，更成為主要投資者之一。除了提供資金外，他也將會把與粉絲交流的經驗，以導師身份和選手們分享。他也對外表示，看好電競項目長期發展的前景，以及選手的熱情，所以決定投資。<br />\n<br />\n金希澈曾在綜藝節目《黃金漁場》（Radio Star）中透露，自己對名牌、名車、名錶等奢侈品都沒有興趣，但在遊戲上花錢毫不手軟。他在節目中表示：「（花錢課金）這樣子遊戲公司賺到錢，才能推出其他遊戲。」更自爆光是在手遊上，就花了超過4000萬韓元。<br />\n<br />\n當時節目主持人金九拉反問：「這麼多錢拿去買錶不是更好？」結果金希澈回應：「看時間的話用手機就可以了。」揭露出電玩迷的價值觀，也被粉絲笑稱是「只在遊戲花錢的哥」。"},{"pid":"aa8edb6389a7341f3057de39b1ff1114f71094a5","tid":2076360,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4959/d4959487.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4959%2Fd4959487.jpg&h=8883deb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SJ希澈（左）是演藝圈出名的電玩迷。（圖／翻攝自vlive）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4959/d4959483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4959%2Fd4959483.jpg&h=0cc9d04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈曾自爆在手遊花了至少4000萬韓元。（圖／翻攝自IG）"},{"pid":"b1fdf314acb03affae25f369f6d1a7a1154d4024","tid":2076360,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4959/d4959484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4959%2Fd4959484.jpg&h=060cd954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈投資電競戰隊，除了資金外還提供與粉絲互動的經驗分享。（圖／翻攝自IG）"},{"pid":"666f41ac4670c0bde4b07a74b513267a6dbc048b","tid":2076360,"uid":45753,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"他在節目中表示：「（花錢課金）這樣子遊戲公司賺到錢，才能推出其他遊戲。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84a6afad7e2c25e11563b44836575ae71f9b918","tid":2076360,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"666f41ac4670c0bde4b07a74b513267a6dbc048b","tid":2076360,"uid":45753,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"他在節目中表示：「（花錢課金）這樣子遊戲公司賺到錢，才能推出其他遊戲。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"電莖師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ad16e0d46529ff04fa7d60f021346f51dd500b","tid":2076360,"uid":203092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"respect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18df18b1991e2003dd3c2d6cf7d85156f027a34b","tid":2076360,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:46:48.000Z","msg":"momo上台唱歌咁辛苦<br />\n你條友係到食軟飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122c4de3698c4f4bec1ecdd8fd52b58a055c207e","tid":2076360,"uid":2784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:47:23.000Z","msg":"課金師"},{"pid":"a57e1afdc81371e47fc46f2545d9a9e260022e7e","tid":2076360,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18df18b1991e2003dd3c2d6cf7d85156f027a34b","tid":2076360,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T12:46:48.000Z","msg":"momo上台唱歌咁辛苦<br />\n你條友係到食軟飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\